  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "x402arcade-api-collection",
    "name": "x402Arcade API",
    "description": "API collection for x402Arcade - a gasless arcade gaming platform on Cronos blockchain.\n\n## Getting Started\n\n1. Set the `baseUrl` variable to your API server (default: http://localhost:3001)\n2. Set the `playerAddress` variable to your test wallet address\n3. For x402 payment testing, you'll need a wallet with devUSDC.e tokens\n\n## Environment Variables\n\n- `baseUrl`: API base URL\n- `playerAddress`: Your Ethereum wallet address\n- `sessionId`: Populated after creating a game session\n\n## x402 Payment Flow\n\nThe `/api/v1/play/:gameType` endpoint uses the x402 payment protocol:\n\n1. Send POST without payment header to get payment requirements\n2. Sign EIP-3009 authorization with your wallet\n3. Send POST with X-Payment header containing the signed auth\n4. Receive sessionId on success",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
